# originator

**Instance Property**

The participant that causes the coordinator to issue the command.

## Declaration

```swift
var originator: AVCoordinatedPlaybackParticipant? { get }
```

## Discussion

Only commands that the system issues on behalf of another participant contain an originator. Local commands to coordinate rate change, or those that originate from a call to [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVDelegatingPlaybackCoordinator/reapplyCurrentItemStateToPlaybackControlDelegate()], don’t.



## Accessing command details

- **expectedCurrentItemIdentifier**: An item identifier the coordinator issues the command for.
